      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and honest ride! This car is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, showing some character through its years of service. While it has some expected wear and tear both inside and out, it remains a solid choice for anyone looking for a functional vehicle at a great value. It's the perfect opportunity to own a quality brand without the premium price tag!",
