    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for over the years. The exterior still looks great with a nice shine, though it does have some minor rock chips on the front bumper and a few light scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains very reliable, with all features functioning as they should, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable and presentable vehicle.",
