    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a persistent engine oil leak and a transmission that hesitates between gears. The exterior shows its age with extensive rust on the wheel arches, several deep scratches, and major paint fading on all upward-facing panels. Inside, the cabin shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components, including the radio and air conditioning. This car would best suit a buyer looking for a dedicated restoration project or a source for spare parts.",
